  "description": "The sixth anime series in the Yu-Gi-Oh! franchise. VRAINS is an acronym for \"Virtual Reality Artificial Intelligence Network System\".\n<br><br>\nIn futuristic Den City, people duel using digital cards in the VR space \"LINK VRAINS\" managed by SOL Technology, Inc. A mysterious organization known as the Knights of Hanoi hacks into LINK VRAINS in search of a runaway AI program, Ignis. One duelist with the username \"Playmaker\" stands against this threat. His true identity is high school student Yuusaku Fujiki, a skilled hacker with a dark past and a grudge against Hanoi. When he becomes the first to capture Ignis, a struggle between Yuusaku, SOL Technology, and the Knights of Hanoi ensues.<br>\n<br>\n(Written by Edo)",
